OL,3,CWhy humidity levels could make the 40C
OL,4,Cheatwave feel even hotter
OL,6,FTemperatures are expected to reach up
OL,7,Fto 40C this week, and while that has
OL,8,Falready led to rare red heat health
OL,9,Falerts in parts of the country, the
OL,10,Fheat is likely to feel even more
OL,11,Fintense.
OL,13,FA major factor of this week's heatwave
OL,14,Fwill be humid air.
OL,16,FWith humidity levels being much higher
OL,17,Fthan usual, conditions will feel
OL,18,Fpretty uncomfortable by day and night.
OL,20,FWhat is humidity?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
