CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1782166688
OL,3,CWhy humidity levels could make the 40C
OL,4,Cheatwave feel even hotter
OL,6,FWhereas when there is relatively
OL,7,Flittle water vapour, it is
OL,8,Fcorrespondingly lower, a dew point of
OL,9,F5C will create dry-feeling air.
OL,11,FWhy does it feel hotter with high
OL,12,Fhumidity?
OL,14,FIt feels hotter because high humidity
OL,15,Fmakes it harder for the body to cool
OL,16,Fitself down.
OL,18,FYour body produces heat, and the main
OL,19,Fway of reducing it is by evaporating
OL,20,Fsweat from your skin.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
