OL,3,CWhy humidity levels could make the 40C
OL,4,Cheatwave feel even hotter
OL,6,FThe humid air will be a major feature
OL,7,Fof this heatwave as we draw in hot,
OL,8,Fmuggy air from Europe and the near
OL,9,FAtlantic.
OL,11,FHot air can hold more moisture from
OL,12,Fthe sea, and is very much a part of
OL,13,Four weather as an island nation.
OL,15,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,16,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,17,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,18,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,20,FWe have the key ingredients for
OL,21,Fhumidity to rise in the coming days.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
