OL,3,CWhy humidity levels could make the 40C
OL,4,Cheatwave feel even hotter
OL,6,FDew point values, which indicate
OL,7,Fhumidity, will be four times as high
OL,8,Fas those during the 40C heatwave in
OL,9,FJuly 2022.
OL,11,FThe air was also significantly drier
OL,12,Fin the historical summer of 1976 as
OL,13,Fheat built from the central and
OL,14,Feastern continents.JWhat does that
OL,15,Fmean this week?
OL,17,FThe UK is expected to feel as humid as
OL,18,Fsome countries nearer the equator,
OL,19,Fsuch as Florida, Singapore and
OL,20,FThailand.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
