OL,3,CWhy humidity levels could make the 40C
OL,4,Cheatwave feel even hotter
OL,6,FWith highs of 38C for consecutive days
OL,7,Fand close to 40C in places, it's
OL,8,Funlikely temperatures will drop below
OL,9,F20-22C in the coming nights.
OL,11,FThis means we're likely to see a
OL,12,Frecord-breaking number of tropical
OL,13,Fnights where temperatures fail to drop
OL,14,Fbelow 20C.
OL,16,FThis heat will make for some
OL,17,Foppressive and stuffy sleeping
OL,18,Fconditions.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
