OL,3,CWhy humidity levels could make the 40C
OL,4,Cheatwave feel even hotter
OL,6,FA day after the summer solstice, night
OL,7,Ftimes are at their shortest this time
OL,8,Fof year, giving even less time for
OL,9,Ftemperatures to recalibrate to more
OL,10,Fcomfortable levels.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/8
